video_title: Do you ever feel burned out?
transcript:
do you ever feel burned out a lot of
people think that they're burned out
because they're doing too much but
that's not the reason why you're burned
out you're not burned out because you're
doing too much you're burned out because
you're not doing enough you're not doing
enough of what makes you happy you're
not doing enough of what fills your soul
you're stuck in the day today and not
doing enough of what makes you feel
alive you're not doing enough of what
really matters to you so if you feel
burned out do more but do more of what
actually makes you feel alive
